1067
01:46:18,639 --> 01:46:25,046
But those phone calls, nothing is going to replace those phone calls, I don't think, in this particular situation.

1068
01:46:26,587 --> 01:46:30,451
Yeah, and if I could make a suggestion, if we are going to stick with

1069
01:46:32,321 --> 01:46:43,185
