1070
01:46:43,205 --> 01:46:49,507
The original reason those numbers published on Thursday is because the state gave us data on Wednesday and

1071
01:46:50,427 --> 01:46:57,752
at the time we cared about what that data said as a marker for what we would do next and none of that applies anymore.

1072
01:46:57,812 --> 01:47:06,778
