1077
01:47:32,745 --> 01:47:35,726
And I would like to see this other information added to that publication.

1078
01:47:36,058 --> 01:47:44,143
Yeah, if there's not a variable that I'm not thinking of, moving it to Monday, I can think of several reasons that that would be advantageous.

1079
01:47:44,243 --> 01:48:01,073
So that would make sense to me, but I think we'll, if it's okay with the committee, discuss this amongst our team over the next day or two, and then see how we can revise some of those systems to make sure the information is more readily accessible.

1080
01:48:02,014 --> 01:48:02,394
Thank you.

