1138
01:53:41,337 --> 01:53:45,400
I know the data we have is based on earlier months in the fall,

1139
01:53:45,800 --> 01:53:49,763
We're seeing extremely high cases that are happening now.

1140
01:53:50,164 --> 01:53:52,586
Students were not tested until last week.

1141
01:53:53,186 --> 01:54:00,632
So we're getting this new information now, but the numbers that are coming in are coming in from Thanksgiving now.

1142
01:54:00,713 --> 01:54:04,075
We still don't know the full brunt of that effect.

1143
01:54:06,984 --> 01:54:11,546
I'm just wondering if someone could respond to that.

1144
01:54:11,566 --> 01:54:17,789
