1145
01:54:18,889 --> 01:54:20,310
I'm sorry you feel that way, Ms.

1146
01:54:20,370 --> 01:54:20,710
Willard.

1147
01:54:21,290 --> 01:54:24,972
I feel I was very clear about what I said earlier.

1148
01:54:25,152 --> 01:54:26,733
We are providing testing.

1149
01:54:27,113 --> 01:54:28,253
Tomorrow's Tuesday.

1150
01:54:28,694 --> 01:54:33,336
So you will have an opportunity as well to participate in testing in your respective building.

1151
01:54:34,696 --> 01:54:41,222
What I did say is I spoke with the instructional leader at the Roberts School with my team.

1152
01:54:41,422 --> 01:54:45,605
We looked at the staff that are placed on quarantine for the time being.

1153
01:54:46,286 --> 01:54:59,376
Some people that have been quarantined are because they've been identified as a close contact within the school or other people who have been quarantined, it's because of a close contact at home.

1154
01:55:00,337 --> 01:55:08,900
And so it's not related to what happened in school, but it could either be exposure at home or exposure within their respective community.

1155
01:55:09,461 --> 01:55:13,682
So we are looking at all of those pieces of data.

1156
01:55:14,262 --> 01:55:21,725
Right now, I know at the Roberts School, five homeroom teachers are currently quarantined.

1157
01:55:22,546 --> 01:55:26,187
One is scheduled to return Friday, another on Thursday.

1158
01:55:26,627 --> 01:55:27,447
So it's a moving,

1159
01:55:29,363 --> 01:55:29,883
schedule.

1160
01:55:30,624 --> 01:55:34,866
